Chou Futsuu Toshi Kashiwa Densetsu: Ekim: Original videos featuring the cast of Chou Futsuu Toshi Kashiwa Densetsu that are supported by the Kashiwa Urban Design Center (UDC2). They are set at Kashiwa Station and are both released online and broadcast at the station.
